# Iris Flower Classifier ðŸŒ¸

A simple machine learning project that uses Random Forest to classify iris flower species based on petal and sepal measurements.

## Dataset
The dataset contains 150 samples with 4 features:
- Sepal Length
- Sepal Width
- Petal Length
- Petal Width

## Model
- RandomForestClassifier from `scikit-learn`
- Accuracy and classification report are printed

## How to Run

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python iris_classifier.py
